title: Nagarjuna is not happy with Akhil's debut film
text: It's already known that Nagarjuna has taken the debut of Akhil rather seriously. And he's been working hard to make sure the film works wonders at the box office as well. Though the release date was finalised, the film was stopped in the last minute as Nagarjuna was not happy with the computer graphics. Well, the film is a socio-fantasy and audiences are bound to have high expectations from the film. So if it falls flat, it will mean a bad debut for Akhil. So Nagarjuna has asked the makers to re-do the bits and it is said that he will be supervising all work personally.
